            <p class="text-brand-slate-gray">Effective Date: July 29, 2025</p>
            <p>Thank you for using PlatesApp.xyz. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and what choices you have.</p>

            <h2>1. What We Collect</h2>
            <p>We may collect:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Information you provide:</strong> Such as your email, profile name, and any photos or comments you upload.</li>
                <li><strong>Technical data:</strong> Your IP address, device type, browser, and how you use the app.</li>
                <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Small files to remember your preferences and keep you logged in.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>2. How We Use Your Info</h2>
            <p>We use your data to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Provide and maintain the service;</li>
                <li>Let you log in and personalize your experience;</li>
                <li>Improve the app by understanding how people use it;</li>
                <li>Contact you with updates or support if needed.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>3. Who We Share It With</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Service providers:</strong> Trusted partners who help run the app (like hosting or analytics tools). They only use your data for what's needed and keep it secure.</li>
                <li><strong>Legal reasons:</strong> If we’re legally required to, or to protect rights and safety.</li>
                <li><strong>Public posts:</strong> If you choose to make your posts public, anyone may see them.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>4. Where We Store Your Info</h2>
            <p>Your data may be stored on secure servers in different countries. By using Plates, you agree to this.</p>

            <h2>5. Children</h2>
            <p>The app is not meant for users under 13. If we learn we’ve collected info from a child, we’ll delete it.</p>

            <h2>6. Your Choices</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Change or delete your info:</strong> You can edit or remove your account any time.</li>
                <li><strong>Email settings:</strong> You can unsubscribe from non-essential emails.</li>
                <li><strong>Delete your account:</strong> Just email us at <a href="mailto:info@platesapp.xyz">info@platesapp.xyz</a> and we’ll help.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>7. Policy Updates</h2>
            <p>If this policy changes, we’ll update it here. You’ll be notified if the changes are important.</p>

